msgid "(Oh... I know where this is)."
msgstr "（哦......我知道这是哪里）。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_FairyRing_B1F_Hallway.event_artist.dlg.aoi"
msgid "This must be under that weird fella's house."
msgstr "这一定是在那个怪人的房子下面。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_FairyRing_B1F_Hallway.event_artist.dlg.aoi"
msgid "You know, the sculptor?"
msgstr "你知道吗，那个雕塑家？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_FairyRing_B1F_Hallway.event_artist.dlg.lacie"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr "嗯。"

msgid "I think artists are really impressive!"
msgstr "我觉得艺术家真的很让人印象深刻！"

msgid "(What's this..?)"
msgstr "（这是什么..？）"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_FairyRing_B1F_Hallway.event_artist.dlg.lacie"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "Not really."
msgstr "不知道呢。"

msgid "Oh, it's a cranky old artist."
msgstr "哦，它是个脾气暴躁的老艺术家。"

msgid "I've never spoken to him because he's in a bad mood when he's tired."
msgstr "我从来没和他说过话，因为他一累的话心情就不好。"

msgid "...And he's almost always tired."
msgstr "...虽然说他一直都很累。"

msgid "But I think artists are really impressive!"
msgstr "但是我觉得艺术家真的很让人印象深刻！"

msgid "Sculpting is really hard..."
msgstr "雕塑是件很难的事情..."

msgid "Especially hands..."
msgstr "特别是要用手这一点..."

msgid "I can't seem to get my hands right..."
msgstr "我的手似乎怎么也弄不好..."

msgid "(Oh, that explains...)"
msgstr "（哦，确实...）"

msgid "(Huh... the path is open now.)"
msgstr "（啊...这条路现在通了。）"

msgid "We need to walk slowly... and uh... keep an eye out."
msgstr "我们要走得慢点...然后，呃...留个心眼。"

msgid "Keep an eye out for what?"
msgstr "为什么要留个心眼？"

msgid "For... fairies."
msgstr "因为...仙子们。"

msgid "Don't you know what this place is!?"
msgstr "你不知道这是什么地方吗！？"

msgid "Lacie, don't you know what this place is!?"
msgstr "莱西，你不知道这是什么地方吗！？"

msgid "...No, not really."
msgstr "...不，我不知道。"

msgid "...!"
msgstr "...！"

msgid "This is the inside of a fairy ring!"
msgstr "这里是仙女环的内部！"

msgid "Lacie, this is the inside of a fairy ring!"
msgstr "莱西，这里是仙女环的内部！"

msgid "Um..."
msgstr "唔..."

msgid "...The mushroom circle from outside?"
msgstr "...是外面那个蘑菇围成的圈圈吗？"

msgid "Yep. That's a fairy ring."
msgstr "对。那就是仙女环。"

msgid "So this place is..."
msgstr "所以这个地方是..."

msgid "Underneath that circle?"
msgstr "圈圈下面？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_FairyRing_B1F_Hallway.event_intro.dlg.aoi"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr "嗯。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_FairyRing_B1F_Hallway.event_intro.dlg.lacie"
msgid "Oh."
msgstr "哦。"

msgid "Can you tell me more?"
msgstr "能细说吗？"

msgid "Let's see... I only know the things everyone talks about."
msgstr "我想想...我只知道大家都在讨论的东西。"

msgid "For one, fairies live in fairy rings, and they're really nasty."
msgstr "首先，仙子们生活在仙女环内，而且它们真的很恶心。"

msgid "(Fairies...)"
msgstr "（仙子们...）"

msgid "They look nasty too, they have this egg-shaped head that's separated from their body, and they're white, and they have big teeth! And some don't have eyes!"
msgstr "它们看起来也很恶心，头是蛋形的，与身体分离，它们全身雪白，牙齿很大！有些还没有眼睛！"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_FairyRing_B1F_Hallway.event_intro.dlg.lacie"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "But even without the fairies, winding up inside of a fairy ring is..."
msgstr "但是即便没有仙子的话，被缠困在仙女环里也是..."

msgid "Well, they say you get stuck here for 7 years."
msgstr "好吧，他们说你会在这里被困7年。"

msgid "But nobody has ever escaped because they usually just die before that."
msgstr "但是没有人曾逃出过，因为他们通常在那之前就死了。"

msgid "Oh god this is horrible, we're not gonna escape!"
msgstr "天呐这太可怕了，我们逃不出去的！"

msgid "Even if we somehow make it 7 years, that's only a myth!"
msgstr "即便我们怎样活了7年，那也不过只是个传说罢了！"

msgid "Maybe it's meant to instill hope in the poor souls that end up here!"
msgstr "也许这只是为了给那些来到这里的可怜人一点希望！"

msgid "LIKE US! THIS IS A DEAD END!!!"
msgstr "像我们的话！已经死定了！！！"

msgid "Aoi."
msgstr "小青。"

msgid "...?"
msgstr "...？"

msgid "Cut it off."
msgstr "再讲就剪烂你的嘴。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_FairyRing_B1F_Hallway.event_intro.dlg.aoi"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "Sorry."
msgstr "对不起。"

msgid "Are the fairies dangerous?"
msgstr "仙子们很危险吗？"

msgid "Yeah..."
msgstr "是的..."

msgid "...But everything is dangerous."
msgstr "...但其实所有东西都很危险。"

msgid "The floor here is also slowly digesting us."
msgstr "这里地板正在缓慢地消化着我们。"

msgid "I guess you don't feel it because you have shoes, hehe..."
msgstr "我猜你感觉不到，因为你穿着鞋子，哈哈..."

msgid "I only have socks, so it's already eating away at them..."
msgstr "我只穿了袜子，所以它已经在蚕食它们了..."

msgid "(Should I offer Aoi my shoes?)"
msgstr "（我要把自己的鞋子给小青吗？）"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_FairyRing_B1F_Hallway.event_intro.choice.(Should I offer Aoi my shoes?)"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_FairyRing_B1F_Hallway.event_intro.choice.(Should I offer Aoi my shoes?)"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "Would you like my shoes?"
msgstr "你想要我的鞋子吗？"

msgid "Whaaat? You're offering me your own shoes?!?"
msgstr "什么？你要给我你的鞋子？！？"

msgid "That's so nice of you!"
msgstr "你真好！"

msgid "That's so nice, Lacie!"
msgstr "你真好，莱西！"

msgid "But no, I'll be alright. I'll just remake my feet if they start being unusable."
msgstr "但是不用了，我没事的。如果我的脚没法走了，我只要重塑一下就可以了。"

msgid "It just burns but that's okay, I'm used to burns."
msgstr "就是有点烫而已，不过没关系，我已经习惯了。"

msgid "...I'm used to burns..."
msgstr "...我以前也被烫过..."

msgid "Um... okay."
msgstr "唔...好吧。"

msgid "(Best not...)"
msgstr "（最好还是不要了...）"

msgid "(Who knows what this floor will do to my feet...)"
msgstr "（谁知道这个地板会对我的脚做什么呢...）"

msgid "(This person is not human, so they will probably be fine.)"
msgstr "（这个人不是人类，所以它应该没事的。）"

msgid "A large skeleton of an unknown creature."
msgstr "未知生物的巨大骨架。"

msgid "Hm...?"
msgstr "唔...？"

msgid "What died here...?"
msgstr "什么东西死在这里了吗...？"

msgid "Something big!"
msgstr "真是个大家伙！"

msgid "Oh!"
msgstr "哦！"

msgid "A dragon!"
msgstr "一条龙！"

msgid "(A dragon...!?)"
msgstr "（一条龙...！？）"

msgid "Was I right?!"
msgstr "我说对了吗？！"

msgid "Huh? How should I know?"
msgstr "啊？我会知道吗？"

msgid "Aw..."
msgstr "哦..."

msgid "A large skeleton of a dragon."
msgstr "一条龙的巨大骨架。"

msgid "(Do dragons really exist in this place...?)"
msgstr "（这个地方真的存在龙吗...？）"

msgid "Isn't it so cool that humans have dragons in their world?"
msgstr "人类的世界里有龙，是不是很酷？"

msgid "I'd like dragons here too."
msgstr "我希望我们这里也能有龙。"

msgid "(Never mind.)"
msgstr "（还是别提起好。）"

msgid "A large skeleton of something other than a dragon."
msgstr "一具巨大的非龙骨架。"

msgid "We sure are walking a lot."
msgstr "我们肯定已经走了很多路了。"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_FairyRing_B1F_Hallway.event_walk_1.dlg.lacie"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "My feet don't hurt, or anything. Don't worry!"
msgstr "我的脚不会疼，也不会出毛病。不要担心！"

msgid "I bet there's no way out..."
msgstr "我敢打赌，这里没有出路..."

msgid "Hmm..."
msgstr "嗯..."

msgid "There's always a way."
msgstr "总会有办法的。"

msgid "(Right...?)"
msgstr "（对吧...？）"

msgid "Whoa."
msgstr "哇哦。"

msgid "I like that!"
msgstr "我喜欢！"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_FairyRing_B1F_Hallway.event_walk_1.dlg.aoi"
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "The path ends here."
msgstr "这条路到此为止。"

msgid "Huh...? Is there really nowhere to go from here...?"
msgstr "啊...？这里真的没有路了吗...？"

msgid "A large bone."
msgstr "巨大的骨头。"

msgid "A broken street lamp."
msgstr "损坏的路灯。"

msgid "Blue mushrooms are lining the floor."
msgstr "蓝色的蘑菇在地板上鳞次栉比。"

msgid "A bunch of rubble."
msgstr "一堆瓦砾。"

msgid "A piece of a sculpture."
msgstr "一座雕塑的碎片。"

msgid "A strangely-shaped pot."
msgstr "造型奇特的壶。"

msgid "There's a large hole on the floor."
msgstr "地板上有个大洞。"

msgid "(It's deep... and dark.)"
msgstr "（很深...而且很黑。）"

msgid "It doesn't seem very smart to try going down there."
msgstr "看起来从这边下去不是个明智的选择。"

msgid "I feel like there has to be a better option than going down this hole..."
msgstr "我感觉比起下去还有更好的选项..."

msgid "(We checked everywhere else but...)"
msgstr "（我们已经调查过别的地方了，但是...）"

msgid "(If I go down there... it will be impossible to come back up...)"
msgstr "（如果我们下去的话...我们就没机会回来了...）"

msgid "Go down the hole?"
msgstr "要下到洞里吗？"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_FairyRing_B1F_Hallway.move_hole.choice.Go down the hole?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgctxt "events.Ch1_FairyRing_B1F_Hallway.move_hole.choice.Go down the hole?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "...Sigh, here we go."
msgstr "...哎，我们走吧。"

msgid "Wanna turn back?"
msgstr "要不回头吧？"

msgid "There's nowhere else to go, so we might as well explore whatever's down there."
msgstr "已经没有别的地方能去了，不如去探索下面的东西。"

msgid "Okay."
msgstr "好吧。"

msgid "Going deeper down to find an exit... this isn't very smart, is it?"
msgstr "深入地下寻找出口...这可不太明智，不是吗？"
